first of all Follow these steps

1 ) install rust plateform 
2 ) Open Terminal
3 ) $ cargo new newproject --bin
4 ) enter
5 ) $ cd newproject
6 ) enter


note! Not try to close terminal just minimize it
  
7 ) Open newproject folder which is show on home
8 ) Open Src folder
9 ) Open main.rs file
10) And start coading
11) After enter coding save file and return on terminal and type cargo run
12) enter
13) The output become on terminal screen

